Last updated: 29 Sep 2025
NameJason Susanto
BirthdayMarch 25, 2004
CountryIndonesia
TeamPaper Rex
  • Twitter
  • Twitch
  • Instagram
  • Steam
  • Youtube

Jason “f0rsakeN” Susanto is a professional VALORANT player from Indonesia who is currently playing for Paper Rex. He is a former professional Counter-Strike: Global Offensive player, where he played for teams such as BOOM Esports in mostly Tier 3 events. He switched to VALORANT when his CS:GO team, Paper Rex, switched to VALORANT.
